msgstr "爆炸当量： {percent:BombLevel}"

#: src/game/server/infclass/classes/humans/human.cpp:1278
msgctxt "Mercenary"
msgid ""
"The bomb is fully upgraded.\n"
"There is nothing to do with the laser."
msgstr ""
"炸弹已经完全充能。\n"
"激光没有用了。"

#: src/game/server/infclass/classes/humans/human.cpp:1287
msgctxt "Mercenary"
msgid ""
"Use the hammer to place a bomb and\n"
"then use the laser to upgrade it"
msgstr "使用锤子放置炸弹, 可用激光升级它"

#: src/game/server/infclass/classes/humans/human.cpp:1302
msgid "The turrets are not allowed by the game rules (at least right now)."
msgstr "游戏规则不允许使用炮塔（至少现在是这样）。"

