#: src/game/server/infclass/classes/humans/human.cpp:2041
msgid "The white hole is ready, use the laser rifle to disrupt space-time"
msgstr "白洞已经就绪, 使用激光枪使空间混乱"

#: src/game/server/infclass/classes/humans/human.cpp:2094
