msgstr "{str:PlayerName} 摧毁了你的炮塔！"

#: src/game/server/infclass/ic_gamecontroller.cpp:99
msgid "Taxi prevents ammo regeneration for all passengers."
msgstr "开车会让所有乘客的弹药停止恢复。"

#: src/game/server/infclass/ic_gamecontroller.cpp:100
msgid "Choosing a random class grants full armor."
msgstr "选择随机职业会获得满盾。"

#: src/game/server/infclass/ic_gamecontroller.cpp:101
msgid "You can toggle hook protection by pressing f3 (\"Vote yes\" keybind)."
msgstr "你能通过按 F3（“赞成投票”键）来切换钩子保护。"

#: src/game/server/infclass/ic_gamecontroller.cpp:102
msgid "Mercenary can reduce ammo usage during flight by tapping instead of holding down the \"fire\" button."
msgstr "雇佣兵能通过连续短暂按下开火键代替长按来节省弹药。"

#: src/game/server/infclass/ic_gamecontroller.cpp:103
msgid "Mercenary's grenades prevent zombies from healing."
msgstr "雇佣兵的榴弹会阻止感染者回血。"

#: src/game/server/infclass/ic_gamecontroller.cpp:104
msgid "Medic can heal Heroes using the grenade launcher."
msgstr "医生能用榴弹发射器治疗英雄。"

#: src/game/server/infclass/ic_gamecontroller.cpp:105
msgid "Medic and Biologist can use hammer to instantly kill an infected."
msgstr "医生和生物学家可以用锤子来瞬间击杀一个感染者。"

#: src/game/server/infclass/ic_gamecontroller.cpp:106
msgid "Hero can stand still for a short time to be pointed towards the flag."
msgstr "英雄能静止不动一段时间，来获得一个指向旗子的点。"

#: src/game/server/infclass/ic_gamecontroller.cpp:107
msgid "Hero's turrets are great for detecting Ghosts."
msgstr "英雄炮塔对于发现幽灵很有用。"

#: src/game/server/infclass/ic_gamecontroller.cpp:108
msgid "Hero's flags fully restore ammo to all humans"
msgstr "英雄旗子能回满所有人类的弹药"

#: src/game/server/infclass/ic_gamecontroller.cpp:109
msgid "Soldier's bombs can hit through walls."
msgstr "士兵炸弹能透过墙壁造成伤害。"

#: src/game/server/infclass/ic_gamecontroller.cpp:110
msgid "Ninja's slash deals 9 damage by default. One more pistol shot will kill an infected with no armor."
msgstr "忍者的斩击默认造成 9 点伤害。再用手枪射击一次就能击杀没有盾的感染者。"

#: src/game/server/infclass/ic_gamecontroller.cpp:111
msgid "Ninja with a single strength upgrade can kill an armorless infected with a single slash."
msgstr "具有强度升级的忍者用一次斩击就能击杀没有盾的感染者。"

#: src/game/server/infclass/ic_gamecontroller.cpp:112
msgid "Ninja doesn't need to directly kill their target. An assist with a laser blind or grenade stun will still grant the rewards."
msgstr "忍者不一定需要直接击杀目标。通过激光致盲或者榴弹冰冻协助队友击杀目标仍能获得奖励。"

#: src/game/server/infclass/ic_gamecontroller.cpp:113
msgid "Ninja heals slightly on a target kill."
msgstr "忍者在击杀目标时会回一点血。"

#: src/game/server/infclass/ic_gamecontroller.cpp:114
msgid "Sniper deals double as much damage in locked position."
msgstr "狙击手在位置锁定时会造成双倍伤害。"

#: src/game/server/infclass/ic_gamecontroller.cpp:115
msgid "Scientist can use Taxi to teleport his teammates into safety."
msgstr "科学家能开车来把队友送到安全的地方。"

#: src/game/server/infclass/ic_gamecontroller.cpp:117
msgid "Scientist can get a white hole after {int:Kills} kill."
msgid_plural "Scientist can get a white hole after {int:Kills} kills."
msgstr[0] "科学家能在 {int:Kills} 个击杀后获得白洞。"

#: src/game/server/infclass/ic_gamecontroller.cpp:122
msgid "Scientist can rocket jump with the laser rifle."
msgstr "科学家可以用激光枪进行榴弹跳。"

#: src/game/server/infclass/ic_gamecontroller.cpp:123
msgid "Biologist's hammer can stop poison effect on teammates. Look for heart icons."
msgstr "生物学家的锤子能解除队友的中毒状态。注意心的图标。"

#: src/game/server/infclass/ic_gamecontroller.cpp:124
msgid "Biologist's bouncy shotgun can be used to hit the infected around corners."
msgstr "生物学家的弹跳霰弹枪能用来攻击角落里的感染者。"

#: src/game/server/infclass/ic_gamecontroller.cpp:125
msgid "Smoker heals by hooking humans."
msgstr "吸烟者可以通过勾人类回血。"

#: src/game/server/infclass/ic_gamecontroller.cpp:126
msgid "Boomer can infect through narrow walls."
msgstr "爆炸者能透过窄墙造成感染。"

#: src/game/server/infclass/ic_gamecontroller.cpp:127
msgid "Hunter receives no knockback from Medic's shotgun."
msgstr "猎人不会被医生霰弹枪击退。"

#: src/game/server/infclass/ic_gamecontroller.cpp:128
msgid "Bat can heal by hitting humans."
msgstr "蝙蝠能通过锤人类回血。"

#: src/game/server/infclass/ic_gamecontroller.cpp:129
msgid "Spider doesn't need to be in Web mode to automatically grab any humans touching its hook."
msgstr "蜘蛛不需要处于网状模式就能自动抓住碰到钩子的人类。"

#: src/game/server/infclass/ic_gamecontroller.cpp:130
msgid "Spider can be hooked and transported by teammates to extend its hook trap."
msgstr "蜘蛛能被队友钩住并移动来增长它的钩子陷阱。"

#: src/game/server/infclass/ic_gamecontroller.cpp:132
msgid "Slug can heal itself and allies over time up to {int:MaxHP} HP with its slime."
msgstr "鼻涕虫和它的队友能站在黏液里来回血（最多 {int:MaxHP} 点）。"

#: src/game/server/infclass/ic_gamecontroller.cpp:136
msgid "Slug can hold down the \"fire\" button to automatically spread slime. The hammer swings won't hurt humans this way though."
msgstr "鼻涕虫能长按开火键来自动散播黏液。这种情况下锤子不会锤到人类。"

#: src/game/server/infclass/ic_gamecontroller.cpp:137
msgid "Voodoo can unfreeze an Undead while in Spirit mode."
msgstr "巫毒者可以在灵魂状态解冻一名不死族。"

#: src/game/server/infclass/ic_gamecontroller.cpp:138
msgid "Witch can spawn the infected through narrow walls."
msgstr "女巫能让感染者透过窄墙出生。"

#: src/game/server/infclass/ic_gamecontroller.cpp:139
msgid "Undead can be removed from a game by throwing it into kill tiles or reviving it as a Medic."
msgstr "通过把不死族扔进刺里或者作为医生治疗它可以消灭一个不死族。"

#: src/game/server/infclass/ic_gamecontroller.cpp:261
msgid "The game is not balanced. Infection is coming."
msgstr "游戏不平衡。感染即将到来。"

#: src/game/server/infclass/ic_gamecontroller.cpp:290
msgid "{str:PlayerName} entered and joined the game"
msgstr "{str:PlayerName} 连接并加入游戏"

#: src/game/server/infclass/ic_gamecontroller.cpp:293
#, fuzzy
msgid "InfectionClass Mod. Version: {str:VerStr}"
msgstr "InfectionClass（感染模式），作者： necropotame（版本 {str:VersionCode}）"

#: src/game/server/infclass/ic_gamecontroller.cpp:295
msgid "See also: /help, /changelog, /about"
msgstr "另见：/help、/changelog、/about"

#: src/game/server/infclass/ic_gamecontroller.cpp:300
