#: src/game/server/infclass/ic_gamecontroller.cpp:4399
msgid "Rules of the game"
msgstr "游戏规则"

#: src/game/server/infclass/ic_gamecontroller.cpp:4401
msgid "InfectionClass is a team game between humans and the infected."
msgstr "InfectionClass（感染模式）是一个人类与感染者间的团队游戏。"

#: src/game/server/infclass/ic_gamecontroller.cpp:4403
msgid "All players start as a human."
msgstr "所有玩家一开始都是人类。"

#: src/game/server/infclass/ic_gamecontroller.cpp:4405
msgid "10 seconds later, a few players become infected."
msgstr "10 秒后，有些玩家会被感染。"

#: src/game/server/infclass/ic_gamecontroller.cpp:4407
msgid "The goal for the humans is to survive until the army cleans the map."
msgstr "人类的目标是生存到援军清理地图。"

#: src/game/server/infclass/ic_gamecontroller.cpp:4409
msgid "The goal for the infected is to infect all humans."
msgstr "感染者目标为感染所有人类。"

#: src/game/server/infclass/ic_gamecontroller.cpp:4411
msgid "See also `/help pages`"
msgstr "另见：/help pages"

#: src/game/server/infclass/ic_gamecontroller.cpp:4416
msgid "How to translate the mod"
msgstr "如何翻译此 mod"

#: src/game/server/infclass/ic_gamecontroller.cpp:4418
msgid "Create an account on Crowdin and join the translation team:"
msgstr "在 Crowdin 上创建一个账户并加入翻译团队:"

#: src/game/server/infclass/ic_gamecontroller.cpp:4425
msgid "White hole"
msgstr "白洞"

#: src/game/server/infclass/ic_gamecontroller.cpp:4427
msgctxt "White hole"
msgid "White hole pulls the infected into its center."
msgstr "白洞把感染者拉进其中心。"

#: src/game/server/infclass/ic_gamecontroller.cpp:4431
msgctxt "White hole"
msgid "Receive it by killing at least {int:NumKills} infected as a Scientist."
msgid_plural "Receive it by killing at least {int:NumKills} of the infected as a Scientist."
msgstr[0] "科学家通过杀死至少 {int:NumKills} 个感染者来获得它。"

#: src/game/server/infclass/ic_gamecontroller.cpp:4435
msgctxt "White hole"
msgid "Use the laser rifle to place it."
msgstr "用激光枪放置它。"

#: src/game/server/infclass/ic_gamecontroller.cpp:4440
msgid "Targeted chat messages"
msgstr "有针对性的聊天消息"

#: src/game/server/infclass/ic_gamecontroller.cpp:4443
msgid "Use “/w <PlayerName> <My Message>” to send a private message to this player."
msgstr "使用 “/w <玩家名> <消息>”给这个玩家发送私聊。"

#: src/game/server/infclass/ic_gamecontroller.cpp:4445
msgid "Use “/msg !<ClassName> <My Message>” to send a private message to all players with a specific class."
msgstr "使用“/msg !<ClassName> <My Message>”给所有特定职业的玩家发送消息。"

#: src/game/server/infclass/ic_gamecontroller.cpp:4447
msgid "Example: “/msg !medic I'm wounded!”"
msgstr "例如：“/msg !medic 我需要治疗！”"

#: src/game/server/infclass/ic_gamecontroller.cpp:4449
msgid "Use “/msg !near” to send a private message to all players near you."
msgstr "使用“/msg !near”给附近所有玩家发送消息。"

#: src/game/server/infclass/ic_gamecontroller.cpp:4454
msgid "Persistent player mute"
msgstr "永久禁言玩家"

#: src/game/server/infclass/ic_gamecontroller.cpp:4457
msgid "Use “/mute <PlayerName>” to mute this player."
msgstr "使用 “/mute <玩家名>” 来屏蔽这个玩家的消息。"

#: src/game/server/infclass/ic_gamecontroller.cpp:4459
msgid "Unlike a client mute this will persist between map changes and wears off when either you or the muted player disconnects."
msgstr "与客户端屏蔽不同，此效果将在地图切换后持续生效，并在您或被屏蔽玩家断开连接时失效。"

#: src/game/server/infclass/ic_gamecontroller.cpp:4461
msgid "Example: “/mute nameless tee”"
msgstr "例如: \"/mute nameless tee\""

#: src/game/server/infclass/ic_gamecontroller.cpp:4467
msgid "How to use taxi mode"
msgstr "如何开车"

#: src/game/server/infclass/ic_gamecontroller.cpp:4469
msgid "Two or more humans can form a taxi."
msgstr "两个或更多的人类可以组成一辆车。"

#: src/game/server/infclass/ic_gamecontroller.cpp:4471
msgid "In order to use it, both humans have to disable hook protection (usually, with F3). The human being hooked becomes the driver."
msgstr "为了开车，两个人都必须取消钩子保护（一般按 F3），然后被勾的人将成为司机。"

#: src/game/server/infclass/ic_gamecontroller.cpp:4473
msgid "To get off the taxi, jump. To drop off your passengers, enable hook protection (usually, with F3)."
msgstr "若要离开车，请跳跃。要从乘客身上下来，可启用钩子保护（通常使用 F3）。"

#: src/game/server/infclass/ic_gamecontroller.cpp:4478
msgid "Fast round"
msgstr "极速回合"

#: src/game/server/infclass/ic_gamecontroller.cpp:4481
msgid "In the fast rounds *more* humans become infected initially, the spawning rate is increased and the round time limit is decreased. White hole is also disabled."
msgstr "在快速回合里，更多的人类会被感染，重生速度会增加，回合时间缩短。白洞被禁用。"

#: src/game/server/infclass/ic_gamecontroller.cpp:4550
msgctxt "Mercenary"
msgid "The Mercenary can fly in the air using their machine gun."
msgstr "雇佣兵可以用手枪飞行。"

#: src/game/server/infclass/ic_gamecontroller.cpp:4551
msgctxt "Mercenary"
msgid "They can also create a powerful bomb with their hammer that can be charged by hitting it or with a laser rifle."
msgstr "他可以用锤子制造强大的炸弹。用锤子或者激光枪可以给炸弹充能。"

#: src/game/server/infclass/ic_gamecontroller.cpp:4555
msgctxt "Mercenary"
msgid "Mercenary can also throw poison grenades that deal {int:NumDamagePoints} damage point and prevent the infected from healing."
msgid_plural "Mercenary can also throw poison grenades that deal {int:NumDamagePoints} damage points and prevent the infected from healing."
msgstr[0] "雇佣兵可以发射毒气弹，使感染者中毒，造成 {int:NumDamagePoints} 点伤害并阻止感染者回血。"

#: src/game/server/infclass/ic_gamecontroller.cpp:4563
msgctxt "Medic"
msgid "The Medic can protect humans with the hammer by giving them armor."
msgstr "医生可以用他的锤子为其他人类增加盾。"

#: src/game/server/infclass/ic_gamecontroller.cpp:4564
msgctxt "Medic"
msgid "Grenades with medicine give armor to everybody in their range, including Heroes and the Medic themself."
msgstr "医生的榴弹可以给在范围里的每个人盾，包括英雄和医生自己。"

#: src/game/server/infclass/ic_gamecontroller.cpp:4569
msgctxt "Medic"
msgid "Tranqulizer rifle makes the infected fall asleep for {sec:Duration}."
msgstr "镇静激光让感染者陷入 {sec:Duration} 沉眠。"

#: src/game/server/infclass/ic_gamecontroller.cpp:4573
msgctxt "Medic"
msgid "Laser rifle revives the infected, but at the cost of 17 hp and armor."
msgstr "激光枪可以治疗感染者，但需要 17 生命或护甲。"

#: src/game/server/infclass/ic_gamecontroller.cpp:4575
msgctxt "Medic"
msgid "Medic also has a powerful shotgun that can knock back the infected."
msgstr "医生的霰弹枪可以击退感染者。"

#: src/game/server/infclass/ic_gamecontroller.cpp:4578
msgctxt "Hero"
msgid "The Hero has all standard weapons."
msgstr "英雄拥有所有标准武器。"

#: src/game/server/infclass/ic_gamecontroller.cpp:4579
msgctxt "Hero"
msgid "The Hero has to find a flag only visible to them. Stand still to be pointed towards it."
msgstr "英雄需要找到只有他可见的旗子。静止不动一段时间，来获得一个指向旗子的点。"

#: src/game/server/infclass/ic_gamecontroller.cpp:4580
msgctxt "Hero"
msgid "The flag gifts a health point, {int:NumArmorGift} armor and full ammo to all humans."
msgstr "旗帜会给所有人类一颗心，{int:NumArmorGift} 点盾，并回满弹药。"

#: src/game/server/infclass/ic_gamecontroller.cpp:4582
msgctxt "Hero"
msgid "It fully heals the Hero and it can grant a turret which you can place down with the hammer."
msgstr "它会回满英雄的血，并使英雄得到一个可用锤子放置的炮塔。"

#: src/game/server/infclass/ic_gamecontroller.cpp:4583
msgctxt "Hero"
msgid "The gift to all humans is only applied when the flag is surrounded by hearts and armor."
msgstr "只有被心和盾包裹的旗帜，才可以为所有人类加成。"

#: src/game/server/infclass/ic_gamecontroller.cpp:4584
msgctxt "Hero"
msgid "The Hero cannot be healed by a Medic, but it can withstand a hit from an infected."
msgstr "英雄不能被医生治疗，但是可以承受一次感染者的攻击而不死。"

#: src/game/server/infclass/ic_gamecontroller.cpp:4587
msgctxt "Engineer"
msgid "The Engineer can build walls with the hammer to block the infected."
msgstr "工程师可以用锤子创建激光墙，阻挡被感染者。"

#: src/game/server/infclass/ic_gamecontroller.cpp:4588
msgctxt "Engineer"
msgid "When an infected touches the wall, it dies."
msgstr "当感染者碰到激光墙时， 它会死亡。"

#: src/game/server/infclass/ic_gamecontroller.cpp:4589
msgctxt "Engineer"
msgid "The lifespan of a wall is {sec:LifeSpan}, and walls are limited to one per player at the same time."
msgstr "激光墙可以存在 {sec:LifeSpan}，每个玩家同时只能拥有一个激光墙。"

#: src/game/server/infclass/ic_gamecontroller.cpp:4594
msgctxt "Soldier"
msgid "The Soldier creates floating bombs with the hammer."
msgstr "士兵可以用锤子放置炸弹。"

#: src/game/server/infclass/ic_gamecontroller.cpp:4597
msgctxt "Soldier"
msgid "Each bomb can explode {int:NumBombs} time."
msgid_plural "Each bomb can explode {int:NumBombs} times."
msgstr[0] "炸弹可以爆炸 {int:NumBombs} 次。"

#: src/game/server/infclass/ic_gamecontroller.cpp:4601
msgid "Use the hammer to place the bomb and explode it multiple times."
msgstr "用锤子放置炸弹并引爆它数次。"

#: src/game/server/infclass/ic_gamecontroller.cpp:4604
msgctxt "Ninja"
msgid "The Ninja can throw flash grenades that can freeze the infected for three seconds."
msgstr "忍者可以用闪光榴弹冻结感染者 3 秒。"

#: src/game/server/infclass/ic_gamecontroller.cpp:4609
msgctxt "Ninja"
msgid "Their hammer is replaced with a katana, allowing them to dash {int:NinjaJump} time before touching the ground."
msgid_plural "Their hammer is replaced with a katana, allowing them to dash {int:NinjaJump} times before touching the ground."
msgstr[0] "他的锤子被武士刀取代，允许他触地后冲刺 {int:NinjaJump} 次。"

#: src/game/server/infclass/ic_gamecontroller.cpp:4615
msgid "They also have a laser rifle that blinds the target for a short period of time."
msgstr "他们还有一把激光枪，可短时间内使目标失明。"

#: src/game/server/infclass/ic_gamecontroller.cpp:4616
msgid "Ninja gets special targets. For killing a target, extra points and abilities are awarded."
msgstr "忍者会得到特殊的目标。当他杀死目标，会获得升级和额外的分数。"

#: src/game/server/infclass/ic_gamecontroller.cpp:4620
msgctxt "Sniper"
msgid "The Sniper can lock the position in mid-air for 15 seconds with the hammer."
msgstr "狙击手可以用锤子在空中锁定自己位置15秒。"

#: src/game/server/infclass/ic_gamecontroller.cpp:4622
msgctxt "Sniper"
msgid "The locked position increases the Sniper's rifle damage from usual 10-13 to 30 damage points."
msgstr "位置锁定将狙击手的激光枪伤害从通常的 10-13 点增加到 20 点。"

#: src/game/server/infclass/ic_gamecontroller.cpp:4624
msgctxt "Sniper"
msgid "They can also jump two times in the air."
msgstr "他可以三段跳。"

#: src/game/server/infclass/ic_gamecontroller.cpp:4627
msgctxt "Scientist"
msgid "The Scientist can pose floating mines with the hammer."
msgstr "科学家可以用锤子放置地雷。"

#: src/game/server/infclass/ic_gamecontroller.cpp:4630
msgctxt "Scientist"
msgid "Mines are limited to {int:NumMines} per player at the same time."
msgid_plural "Mines are limited to {int:NumMines} per player at the same time."
msgstr[0] "每个玩家同时可放置最多 {int:NumMines} 个地雷。"

#: src/game/server/infclass/ic_gamecontroller.cpp:4633
msgctxt "Scientist"
msgid "Scientist has also grenades that teleport them."
msgstr "科学家有用于瞬移的榴弹枪。"

#: src/game/server/infclass/ic_gamecontroller.cpp:4634
msgctxt "Scientist"
msgid "A lucky Scientist devoted to killing can get a white hole that sucks the infected in which can be placed with the laser rifle."
msgstr "幸运的科学家会在杀死感染者时得到白洞，白洞可用激光枪放置，会吸住感染者。"

#: src/game/server/infclass/ic_gamecontroller.cpp:4638
msgctxt "Biologist"
msgid "The Biologist has a shotgun with bouncing bullets and can create a spring laser trap by shooting with the laser rifle."
msgstr "生物学家可以用霰弹枪射出跳弹，也可以用激光枪设置激光陷阱。"

#: src/game/server/infclass/ic_gamecontroller.cpp:4640
msgctxt "Biologist"
msgid "They are also immune to continuous poison effect, and can stop it on teammates with the Hammer."
msgstr "他们不会受到持续的毒伤害，并且能用锤子解除队友的中毒状态。"

#: src/game/server/infclass/ic_gamecontroller.cpp:4644
msgctxt "Looper"
msgid "The Looper has a laser wall that slows down the infected and a low-range laser rifle with a high fire rate."
msgstr "循环者有激光墙，可以减慢感染者的速度，还有一支射速高的低射程激光枪。"

#: src/game/server/infclass/ic_gamecontroller.cpp:4646
msgctxt "Looper"
msgid "They can also jump two times in the air."
msgstr "他可以三段跳。"

#: src/game/server/infclass/ic_gamecontroller.cpp:4649
msgctxt "Smoker"
msgid "Smoker has a powerful hook that hurts humans and sucks their blood, restoring the Smoker's health."
msgstr "吸烟者有一个强大的钩子，通过伤害人类，来恢复吸烟者的血量。"

#: src/game/server/infclass/ic_gamecontroller.cpp:4651
msgctxt "Smoker"
msgid "It can also infect humans and heal the infected with the hammer."
msgstr "它可以用锤子感染人类或治疗感染者。"

#: src/game/server/infclass/ic_gamecontroller.cpp:4654
msgctxt "Boomer"
msgid "The Boomer explodes when it attacks."
msgstr "爆炸者在攻击的时候会自爆。"

#: src/game/server/infclass/ic_gamecontroller.cpp:4655
msgctxt "Boomer"
msgid "All humans affected by the explosion become infected."
msgstr "人类会被爆炸感染。"

#: src/game/server/infclass/ic_gamecontroller.cpp:4656
msgctxt "Boomer"
msgid "It can also inflict 1 damage point per second by hooking humans."
msgstr "它可以勾住人类，每秒造成 1 点伤害。"

#: src/game/server/infclass/ic_gamecontroller.cpp:4659
msgctxt "Hunter"
msgid "The Hunter can jump two times in the air and has some resistance to knock-backs."
msgstr "猎人可以三段跳，并且有击退抗性。"

#: src/game/server/infclass/ic_gamecontroller.cpp:4661
msgctxt "Hunter"
msgid "It can infect humans and heal the infected with the hammer."
msgstr "它可以用锤子感染人类或治疗感染者。"

#: src/game/server/infclass/ic_gamecontroller.cpp:4662
msgctxt "Hunter"
msgid "It can also inflict 1 damage point per second by hooking humans."
msgstr "它可以勾住人类，每秒造成 1 点伤害。"

#: src/game/server/infclass/ic_gamecontroller.cpp:4665
msgctxt "Bat"
msgid "Bat can jump endlessly in the air but it cannot infect humans."
msgstr "蝙蝠能够在空中无限跳跃，但是不能直接感染人类。"

#: src/game/server/infclass/ic_gamecontroller.cpp:4666
msgctxt "Bat"
msgid "Instead, it can hammer humans to steal their health and heal itself."
msgstr "相反，他可以锤人类来窃取人类的血量并且回血。"

#: src/game/server/infclass/ic_gamecontroller.cpp:4667
msgctxt "Bat"
msgid "The hammer is also useful for healing the infected."
msgstr "锤子可以治疗感染者。"

#: src/game/server/infclass/ic_gamecontroller.cpp:4668
msgctxt "Bat"
msgid "It can also inflict 1 damage point per second by hooking humans."
msgstr "他可以勾住人类，每秒造成 1 点伤害。"

#: src/game/server/infclass/ic_gamecontroller.cpp:4671
msgctxt "Ghost"
msgid "The Ghost is invisible until a human comes nearby, it takes damage, or it uses the hammer."
msgstr "幽灵在旁边无人类时会隐形，除非受到伤害或者使用锤子。"

#: src/game/server/infclass/ic_gamecontroller.cpp:4673
msgctxt "Ghost"
msgid "It can infect humans and heal the infected with the hammer."
msgstr "它可以用锤子感染人类或治疗感染者。"

#: src/game/server/infclass/ic_gamecontroller.cpp:4674
msgctxt "Ghost"
msgid "It can also inflict 1 damage point per second by hooking humans."
msgstr "它可以勾住人类，每秒造成 1 点伤害。"

#: src/game/server/infclass/ic_gamecontroller.cpp:4677
msgctxt "Spider"
msgid "The Spider has a web hook that automatically grabs any human touching it."
msgstr "蜘蛛有网状钩子，可以抓住碰到钩子的人类。"

#: src/game/server/infclass/ic_gamecontroller.cpp:4678
msgctxt "Spider"
msgid "The web hook mode can be toggled by switching the weapon."
msgstr "通过切换武器可以切换钩子模式。"

#: src/game/server/infclass/ic_gamecontroller.cpp:4679
msgctxt "Spider"
msgid "In both modes the hook inflicts 1 damage point per second and can grab a human for longer."
msgstr "在两种模式里钩子都可以给人类每秒造成 1 点伤害，并且可长时间勾住人类。"

#: src/game/server/infclass/ic_gamecontroller.cpp:4683
msgctxt "Ghoul"
msgid "The Ghoul can devour anything that has died nearby, which makes it stronger, faster and more resistant."
msgstr "食尸鬼可以吞食它附近已经死亡的感染者，使它更快，更壮，更强。"

#: src/game/server/infclass/ic_gamecontroller.cpp:4685
msgctxt "Ghoul"
msgid "It digests the fodder over time, going back to the normal state. Some nourishment is also lost on death."
msgstr "它会逐渐消耗饱食度直到回到初始状态，死亡会失去部分饱食度。"

#: src/game/server/infclass/ic_gamecontroller.cpp:4687
msgctxt "Ghoul"
msgid "Ghoul can infect humans and heal the infected with the hammer."
msgstr "食尸鬼可以用锤子感染人类或治疗感染者。"

#: src/game/server/infclass/ic_gamecontroller.cpp:4688
msgctxt "Ghoul"
msgid "It can also inflict 1 damage point per second by hooking humans."
msgstr "它可以勾住人类，每秒造成 1 点伤害。"

#: src/game/server/infclass/ic_gamecontroller.cpp:4691
msgctxt "Slug"
msgid "The Slug can make the ground and walls toxic by spreading slime with the hammer."
msgstr "鼻涕虫可以用锤子向地面和墙壁散播粘液，让它们变得有毒。"

#: src/game/server/infclass/ic_gamecontroller.cpp:4692
msgctxt "Slug"
msgid "The slime heals the infected and deals damage to humans."
msgstr "粘液会治疗感染者并对人类造成伤害。"

#: src/game/server/infclass/ic_gamecontroller.cpp:4693
msgctxt "Slug"
msgid "Slug can infect humans and heal the infected with the hammer."
msgstr "鼻涕虫可以用锤子感染人类或治疗感染。"

#: src/game/server/infclass/ic_gamecontroller.cpp:4694
msgctxt "Slug"
msgid "It can also inflict 1 damage point per second by hooking humans."
msgstr "它可以勾住人类，每秒造成 1 点伤害。"

#: src/game/server/infclass/ic_gamecontroller.cpp:4697
msgctxt "Voodoo"
msgid "The Voodoo does not die immediately when killed but instead enters Spirit mode for a short time."
msgstr "巫毒者不会在被杀死时立刻死亡，而是进入短暂的灵魂状态。"

#: src/game/server/infclass/ic_gamecontroller.cpp:4699
msgctxt "Voodoo"
msgid "While in Spirit mode it cannot be killed. When the time is up it finally dies."
msgstr "在灵魂状态下无法被击杀。当时间结束它才会死亡。"

#: src/game/server/infclass/ic_gamecontroller.cpp:4700
msgctxt "Voodoo"
msgid "Voodoo can infect humans and heal the infected with the hammer."
msgstr "巫毒者可以用锤子感染人类或治疗感染者。"

#: src/game/server/infclass/ic_gamecontroller.cpp:4701
msgctxt "Voodoo"
msgid "It can also inflict 1 damage point per second by hooking humans."
msgstr "它可以勾住人类，每秒造成 1 点伤害。"

#: src/game/server/infclass/ic_gamecontroller.cpp:4704
msgctxt "Witch"
msgid "The Witch can provide a spawn point for the infected."
msgstr "女巫可以为感染者提供一个出生点。"

#: src/game/server/infclass/ic_gamecontroller.cpp:4705
msgctxt "Witch"
msgid "If the Witch dies, it disappears and is replaced by another class."
msgstr "如果女巫死了，它会消失并转变职业。"

#: src/game/server/infclass/ic_gamecontroller.cpp:4706
msgctxt "Witch"
msgid "Witch can infect humans and heal the infected with the hammer."
msgstr "女巫可以用锤子感染人类或治疗感染者。"

#: src/game/server/infclass/ic_gamecontroller.cpp:4707
msgctxt "Witch"
msgid "It can also inflict 1 damage point per second by hooking humans."
msgstr "它可以勾住人类，每秒造成 1 点伤害。"

#: src/game/server/infclass/ic_gamecontroller.cpp:4710
msgctxt "Undead"
msgid "The Undead cannot die. Instead of dying, it gets frozen for 10 seconds."
msgstr "不死族不会死亡，而是被冻结 10 秒。"

#: src/game/server/infclass/ic_gamecontroller.cpp:4711
msgctxt "Undead"
msgid "If an infected heals it, the freeze effect disappears."
msgstr "如果一个感染者锤它，冻结效果会消失。"

#: src/game/server/infclass/ic_gamecontroller.cpp:4712
msgctxt "Undead"
msgid "Undead can infect humans and heal the infected with the hammer."
msgstr "不死族可以用锤子感染人类或治疗感染。"

#: src/game/server/infclass/ic_gamecontroller.cpp:4713
msgctxt "Undead"
msgid "It can also inflict 1 damage point per second by hooking humans."
msgstr "它可以勾住人类，每秒造成 1 点伤害。"

#: src/game/server/infclass/ic_gamecontroller.cpp:4861
msgid "You have killed a witch, +5 points"
msgstr "你杀了一个女巫，+5 分"

#: src/game/server/infclass/ic_gamecontroller.cpp:4865
msgid "You have killed an undead! +5 points"
msgstr "你杀了一个不死族，+5 分"

#: src/game/server/infclass/ic_gamecontroller.cpp:4986
msgid "The witch is dead"
